data.description: Welcome to 46731 Al Mar St. located in the Rainieri Run Subdivision, a quiet and quaint neighborhood in the Lexington Park area. This is a charming 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home that seamlessly blends modern updates and is minutes from PAX River Naval Air Station. As you walk into this beautiful home you will find a spacious floor plan with a combination of hardwood floors and carpet throughout. The home has a two-car garage spacious enough for extra storage. The main floor features a living room, a fireplace, and the kitchen open to a spacious family room. The kitchen flows into the dining room which is a great way to host family and friends or even have more intimate gatherings! Upstairs you will be drawn to a generous owner’s suite with a large walk-in closet. The home also has four other bedrooms and a full bathroom for the comfort of family and guest. The home also has a walk-out basement that is fully finished with a wet bar awaiting your personal touches! You will be close to shopping, dining, and local farmer’s markets in the area and less than 15 mins. away from Solomon’s Island with great restaurants, seasonal concerts, watersports, fishing and much more! Don’t miss out on the chance to make this extraordinary property your own! Schedule a showing and experience the 46731 Al Mar St. property for yourself! Seller Prefers Cardinal Title Group.
